# Environment Variables for Chipi AI Virtual Assistant

# ================================
# REQUIRED ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# ================================

# Google Gemini AI API Key
# Get your API key from: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
# This is required for AI functionality
VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# ================================
# OPTIONAL ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# ================================

# Development/Production mode
# Automatically set by Vite
# NODE_ENV=development

# ================================
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# ================================

# 1. Copy this file to .env:
#    cp .env.example .env

# 2. Get your Gemini API key:
#    - Visit https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
#    - Create a new API key
#    - Copy the key

# 3. Replace 'your_gemini_api_key_here' with your actual API key

# 4. Save the .env file

# ⚠️  IMPORTANT SECURITY NOTES:
# - Never commit .env files to version control
# - Keep your API keys secret and secure
# - Use different API keys for development and production
# - Regenerate API keys if compromised

# ================================
# DEPLOYMENT CONFIGURATION
# ================================

# For Vercel Deployment:
# Set environment variables in Vercel Dashboard:
# Dashboard → Settings → Environment Variables
# Add: VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY = your_actual_api_key

# For Other Platforms:
# Ensure VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY is set in your deployment environment
